@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rinuaj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.68 - v1 + 0.13) / wp.sin(v0 + 0.74)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos(1.00))
    tmp = wp.exp((0.69 - v2))
    v1 = v0
    v2 = (v0 * ((v0 + 0.97 + v1 + 0.45) / (v2 + 0.04 - v0 + 0.63)))
    data[tid] = v0
